          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Customize with AI</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Use our AI assistant to generate compelling copy, optimize subject lines, and personalize content.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full gradient-bg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mx-auto mb-6 text-white">3</div>
